discourse_list.title: I have some sai that needs migrated I'm lost

content.content: I was messing around with dapps and came across makerdao dapp I clicked on it and connected my wallet that had some old sai on it which I didn’t have a clue how so when I connected my wallet next screen came up said something like claim my cdps or peth or such and the other said collect sai I had no clue so I dug into it checking it out I’m lost it’s not much says to claim your peth so I tried to do this and when did my gas fee was higher then the claim which I have no Ethereum anyways so that was at a lost clicked on other options and nothing same thing no gas fee i also I forgot to mention that the bite option came up and said I owe a dept not sure how that’s possible or what happened or what’s up with that I don’t recall borrowing anything whatsoever I’m really lost and I sure don’t want any debts I have enough and I’m struggling as I type this enough what can I do here to fix this my conscience’s is terrible when I owe something  to anyone or bill but I’m very lost I’m sorry folks I do apologize Stay safe much appreciated looking for anything that can help my finances  that are depleting fast  this is why I’m curious to know just about anything I can to get back up ahead

If you have Sai you can redeem it for ETH here: https://migrate.makerdao.com/ - This is the official migration portal. Be careful if you are using any other dapp that claims to handle migration - it could very likely be a scam site.

Yeah as I’ve mentioned  in this post it actually is’nt worth the transaction amount claimed would be less then gas fee and I haven’t any Ethereum to do this trade and if i did I’d probably just exchange and provide liquidity some how thanks for reply
